paragraphs: Hello, my name is Sangwoo Park, and I am an undergraduate student at Yonsei University. I'm currently majoring in Computer Science. My current GPA is 4.11/4.3. I am planning to follow career in AI research. From 2023.7 ~ 2024.7 I participated as research intern in DLI Lab in jinyeong yeo's NLP group in Yonsei. My interest lies on multimodal learning, embodied agent decision making, reinforcement learning, and natural language processing.
